content: We expect full year net franchises sold of approximately 1,500 compared to our prior guidance of 1,000; full year net initial studio openings of approximately 1,000 and we expect the cadence of those openings to be weighted towards the back half of the year; full year revenue between $255 million and $275 million; full year adjusted EBITDA between $90 million and $100 million; and full year free cash flow between $50 million and $60 million.
